{"tid":83384,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲想踢好波但完全冇運動天份可以點","createTime":"2017-01-16T16:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T08:18:52.000Z","uid":66189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efb09f6f00576704dc47e8a4c7602184654c88d3","tid":83384,"uid":66189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"想踢波好少少<br />\n間唔中有去tan下腳<br />\n不過波都控唔穩<br />\n位置又錯哂，成日九跑都冇咩效果<br />\n反應好慢，俾人一爆就甩<br />\n上過大班人既足球班<br />\n進步好細<br />\n可以點搞<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話要踢到識飛<br />\n只係想可以踢下街場<br />\n唔太失禮已經好滿足<br />\n<br />\n巴打們有咩建議"},{"pid":"a79ad78c3e4f12d9a17f2a276a9dae39e0575269","tid":83384,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:29:59.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"7fd6c371adba0f1acd4bd713dfb00ea4b35a9010","tid":83384,"uid":27321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b790199781512c0a69535e5e5bf923e929126356","tid":83384,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"斬掉重練"},{"pid":"6814537d47ba7d24d341b12179ca9698fdaf5a4d","tid":83384,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"試下練插水"},{"pid":"eae496e94323cf5d2425d5800bd165ef0dff60f8","tid":83384,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"玩下姐，唔好太認真<br />\n享受就得啦"},{"pid":"6097d19fe261c31d8f6cb582589f163f7641197c","tid":83384,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"fifa"},{"pid":"4d051e32cd154d404c5ca01bd6d3b2d53b731d36","tid":83384,"uid":66189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁直接啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcc37a01bec42b5cbb2c