63a2906","tid":83384,"uid":62097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"踢多啲 一路踢一路用腦諗要點做"},{"pid":"529afed223d4145d48a4b65aeb6a7160ad23f28c","tid":83384,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"30 歲大部人應該都係用返咁多年踢波經驗去踢，<br />\n體能冇乜可能keep到，<br />\n如果宜家先學踢，但又冇可能擺到好多時間去練<br />\n所以應該冇乜可能"},{"pid":"0acd340305dc6f165075d6e526e4709006627f76","tid":83384,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:52:34.000Z","msg":"認真第一唔好驚波先，第二接波前望人唔好dup低頭<br />\n<br />\n練控波可以試下對住牆練，到練熟左可以試下一野ban個波去牆到，控佢反彈果野<br />\n<br />\n練控高波可以自己一野踢個波上天有咁高得咁高，然後試下控返落黎，用心口，用頭，用腳咁<br />\n<br />\n不過最重要係踢多啲，觀察下人地點做然後模仿。巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378104eefee81e2f171b917b31e2278e120fc1a2","tid":83384,"uid":35474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"陪我踢 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2818b4cc22b9b00b3495e021318c604c50f8441e","tid":83384,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"打機算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}